external_knowledge:
- "Diverse hardware ecosystem" refers to the variety of hardware components (CPUs and GPUs) used by manufacturers;
- "Top three" means the manufacturers with the highest ranks in terms of the total number of distinct components;
- "Distinct components" refers to unique CPU and GPU models.

sql:
SELECT cpu_name, cpu_speed
FROM cpus
ORDER BY cpu_speed DESC;

SELECT manufacturer_name, contact_email
FROM manufacturers
WHERE manufacturer_id = (SELECT MIN(manufacturer_id) FROM manufacturers);
